1 Data prep

1.1 Load libraries

library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(tibble)
library(here)
library(tidyr)
library(rstan);options(mc.cores = parallel::detectCores())
library(QM);#devtools::install_github("gledguri/QM",force = T)
library(MoMAColors);#devtools::install_github("BlakeRMills/MoMAColors");require(MoMAColors)
library(ggu.base.fun);#devtools::install_github('gledguri/ggednasd/ggu.base.fun',force = T)

1.2 Load data

amp_eff_mock1 <- readRDS(here('../Mock_v1/Output/amp_eff_param_mock_1_all_sp.rds'))
amp_eff_mock2 <- readRDS(here('../Mock_v2_v3_v4/Output/amp_eff_param_mock_2_all_sp.rds'))
amp_eff_mock3 <- readRDS(here('../Mock_v2_v3_v4/Output/amp_eff_param_mock_3_all_sp.rds'))
amp_eff_mock4 <- readRDS(here('../Mock_v2_v3_v4/Output/amp_eff_param_mock_4_all_sp.rds'))

1.3 Curate data

# Pivot mocks wider
amp_eff_mock1_w <- amp_eff_mock1 %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = mock_type, values_from = alpha)
amp_eff_mock2_w <- amp_eff_mock2 %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = mock_type, values_from = alpha)
amp_eff_mock3_w <- amp_eff_mock3 %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = mock_type, values_from = alpha)
amp_eff_mock4_w <- amp_eff_mock4 %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = mock_type, values_from = alpha)
# Combine (join) mocks together
all_mock_w <- amp_eff_mock1_w %>% column_to_rownames('Species') %>% 
  custom_cbind(.,
               amp_eff_mock2_w %>% column_to_rownames('Species')
               ) %>% 
  custom_cbind(.,
               amp_eff_mock3_w %>% column_to_rownames('Species')
               ) %>% 
  custom_cbind(.,
               amp_eff_mock4_w %>% column_to_rownames('Species')
               )

# Show all mocks
all_mock_w %>% rownames_to_column() %>% 
  as_tibble()

# â¹ 29 more rows
# Pivot all mocks longer
all_mock <- all_mock_w %>% 
  rownames_to_column('Species') %>% 
  pivot_longer(cols = M1_even:M4_skew,
               names_to = 'mock_type',
               values_to='alpha')

# Filter the NA's
all_mock <- all_mock %>% 
  filter(!is.na(alpha))
saveRDS(all_mock,here('Output/amp_eff_param_all_mocks_all_sp.rds'))

1.4 Plot alphas

#all mocks
ggplot(data = all_mock)+
    geom_jitter(aes(y=Species,x=alpha,color=mock_type),
                width = 0,
                height = 0.1)+
    ggtitle('All mocks (1 - 4) even vs skew')+
    scale_color_manual(values = moma.colors("Lupi",n = le(all_mock$mock_type)))+
    theme_bw()+
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0,
                         linetype = "dashed",
                         color = 'black',
                         linewidth=0.2)+
    labs(x = "Alpha", y = "Species")
# Different scale
ggplot(data = all_mock)+
    geom_jitter(aes(y=Species,x=alpha,color=mock_type),
                width = 0,
                height = 0.1)+
    ggtitle('All mocks (1 - 4) even vs skew')+
    scale_color_manual(values = moma.colors("Lupi",n = le(all_mock$mock_type)))+
    theme_bw()+
  xlim(-0.02,0.04)+
    geom_vline(xintercept = 0,
                         linetype = "dashed",
                         color = 'black',
                         linewidth=0.2)+
    labs(x = "Alpha", y = "Species")
